---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import projectImage from "../../assets/devgpt.svg";
---

<div class="group flex-[1_0_calc(100%_-12px)] md:flex-[1_0_calc(50%_-12px)] relative rounded-2xl border border-secondary overflow-hidden">
		<Image src={projectImage} alt="Project image" class="absolute h-full w-full object-cover rounded-2xl blur-sm brightness-50 -z-10" />
		<div class="space-y-6 p-6">
			<h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold md:text-3xl">DevGPT</h3>
			<div class="flex gap-3 flex-wrap">
				<div class="inline-block rounded border border-primary bg-secondary py-1 px-2 text-text">GitBook</div>
			</div>
			<p>Pipeline Tool Designed for Teams that Seamlessly Integrates with Leading Ticket Systems; Over 31% of Pull Requests Merged First Time Across Diverse Projects.</p>
		</div>
</div>
